cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.CV 

This paper deals with generating adversarial examples for text classification tasks using optimization techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves optimization techniques, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with security and attacks, which could place it in cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Finally, the paper involves image and audio samples, which could suggest a connection to cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition).
